{"tid":1932604,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"覺唔覺《於心有愧》最後個句好奇怪","createTime":"2020-03-18T22:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T02:27:26.000Z","uid":207111,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db5ffed62715b330e7f7fb9be423005a26130989","tid":1932604,"uid":207111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:37:01.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅既於心有愧<br />\n明明成首歌好好聽 詞又唔錯<br />\n硬係最尾個句 仍想你一家可到齊 怪怪地<br />\n無喇喇好似咒人全家死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要個音樂已經完咗 好似夾硬突咗一句出黎咁<br />\n次次聽完個Outro都要快啲飛 避開呢句<br />\n究竟呢句係咪有咩特別意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab6a0f1f8c14736dcfb7734daa42afd4102b4be","tid":1932604,"uid":7270,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:41:15.000Z","msg":"講前一句話想自己某日能安息於葬禮喎～<br />\n我諗即係佢希望人地可以一家到齊瞻仰遺容令佢可以安息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c8216e8e2d1045cd34480848f8c3496ba62d99","tid":1932604,"uid":185565,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:42:21.000Z","msg":"唔覺 咪想人去拜自己<br />\n至於係情人定自己老母隨你了"},{"pid":"f0228f13d3ccbdbe80290ea59e15e4d52a8f3d97","tid":1932604,"uid":189109,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:45:37.000Z","msg":"其實係一個老母奉子成婚 之後再婚嘅故事"},{"pid":"536c8c4286179df3c7519e466efed0d37ec6337d","tid":1932604,"uid":65289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c8216e8e2d1045cd34480848f8c3496ba62d99","tid":1932604,"uid":185565,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:42:21.000Z","msg":"唔覺 咪想人去拜自己<br />\n至於係情人定自己老母隨你了"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T22:47:26.000Z","msg":"即係有一日老母拉大隊全家去大酒店話個舊朋友瓜左<br />\n但係其實呢條撚樣以前害到你老母好唔開心好有陰影既咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f615bc18aa9a4c9adb5efaf4